sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server
    participant IntermCA as Intermediate CA
    participant RootCA as Root CA (Trust Store)
    participant OCSP as OCSP Responder

    Client->>Server: ClientHello (TLS handshake start)
    Server-->>Client: ServerHello + Certificate chain
    Note over Client: Parse certificate fields\n(subject, issuer, validity, SANs)
    Client->>Client: Check hostname matches CN or SAN
    Client->>Client: Check notBefore <= now <= notAfter
    Client->>IntermCA: Verify server cert signature\nusing intermediate CA public key
    IntermCA-->>Client: Signature valid
    Client->>RootCA: Verify intermediate CA cert\nusing root CA public key
    RootCA-->>Client: Root CA found in trust store
    Client->>OCSP: Check revocation status\n(certificate serial number)
    OCSP-->>Client: Certificate status: good
    Note over Client: All checks passed\nProceed with key exchange
    Client->>Server: Continue TLS handshake
